com.couchbase.lite

Class MutableArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.couchbase.lite.Array
      • com.couchbase.lite.MutableArray
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FLEncodable, Iterable<Object>

    public final class MutableArray
extends Array
    MutableArray provides access to array data. This class and its constructor are referenced by name, from native code.
